---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';

const updated = 'July 16, 2026';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | Speedy Gonzalez Roofing"
  description="How Speedy Gonzalez Roofing collects, uses, and protects your information."
  path="/privacy"
  breadcrumbs={[{ href: '/privacy', label: 'Privacy Policy' }]}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lede">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p>
        This policy explains what we collect when you use speedygonzalezroofing.com, why we
        collect it, and what we do with it. If you have questions, call {business.phones.office}
        or email <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you fill out our estimate form, we collect what you type into it:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Your phone number</li>
        <li>Your zip code</li>
        <li>The service you need and anything else you tell us</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        If you call us, we may keep a record of your name, number, and what you called about.
      </p>

      <h2>Why we collect it</h2>
      <p>
        To contact you about your roof. That is it. We use your details to schedule your free
        inspection, send your estimate, and follow up on your job.
      </p>

      <h2>Do you sell my information?</h2>
      <p>
        No. We do not sell, rent, or trade your information to anyone. We do not hand your
        details to lead brokers or other contractors.
      </p>
      <p>
        We share information only with people who help us run the business, such as the service
        that delivers our form submissions, and only as much as they need. We also share
        information if the law requires it.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
      <p>
        This site is a set of static pages. We do not use advertising cookies or third-party
        trackers to follow you around the internet.
      </p>

      <h2>Text messages</h2>
      <p>
        If you give us your number, we may text you about your estimate or your job. You can
        stop those any time by replying STOP. See our
        <a href="/sms-terms">SMS terms and conditions</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You can ask us what we have about you, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete it.
        Call {business.phones.office} or email
        <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a> and we will take care of it.
      </p>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        This site is for adults hiring a roofer. We do not knowingly collect information from
        children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>
        If we change this policy, we update the date at the top of this page. Big changes get
        posted here.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact us</h2>
      <address>
        {business.name}<br />
        {business.address.street}<br />
        {business.address.city}, {business.address.state} {business.address.zip}<br />
        {business.phones.office}<br />
        <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a>
      </address>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .narrow {
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  address {
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
